# Cross-Validated MCP- or SCAD-penalized Classification Learner

MCP- or SCAD-penalized binary classification model with k-fold cross
validation for choosing the regularization parameter lambda. Calls
[`ncvreg::cv.ncvreg()`](https://pbreheny.github.io/ncvreg/reference/cv.ncvreg.html)
from package [ncvreg](https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=ncvreg) with
`family` set to `"binomial"`. Covariates are internally standardized by
`ncvreg` prior to model fitting.

## Dictionary

instantiated via
[lrn()](https://mlr3.mlr-org.com/reference/mlr_sugar.html):
